title: Luxury Apartments Near DT Austin and 6th St (East Austin)
posting_body: ['Enjoy the very best of what Austin has to offer by being mere minutes away from the heart of downtown.', 'You are seconds away from Whole Foods, Target, and many other wonderful shops in East Austin.', '🛒', 'Grab a drink and enjoy Austin’s amazing night night by living only one street away from Austin’s famous East 6th street  with many amazing bars to frequent and enjoy such as Latch Key, Hotel Vegas, Shangri-la and Whisler’s 🍻', 'Amazing amenities include:', '🏋️\u200d♂️ 24/7 fitness center with all the weights you could need', '🏊2 gorgeous swimming pools survive those brutal summers with multiple grills, and lounge chairs to kick back on', '🐶Dog parks, and a wonderful area with many shops to explore with your furry friend.', 'Every uniquely designed apartment home contains a gourmet-style kitchen and spa-inspired bathroom, with wood-style plank flooring throughout the living spaces.', '✨', 'Call/Text Mike at', 'show contact info', 'to schedule a showing !', 'Not what you’re looking for?', 'Let me help you find what you need :)', 'I am an apartment locator with unparalleled market knowledge that specializes in making sure you find the perfect apartment to fit your needs.', 'Let me use my experience to make your search easier.', "Oh, did I mention it's completely FREE for you?", 'Servicing all of Austin!', 'Mike Gonzalez', 'Apartment Specialist', 'Licensed Realtor', 'Contact me at', 'show contact info', 'and thank yourself in the next year :)']
